<p>The appropriately named F-class star lights up the high-tech facilities of Eavesdown Docks. Constructed in the late stages of the Colonia Expansion Initiative by the Browncoats, this system on the fringes of the region is a substantial producer of a wide range of commodities for the nearby industries.</p>
<p>Following expensive and largely unsuccessful attempts to expand their operations, the Browncoats decided to restrict their operations solely to the White Sun system in February 3304 â€“ although fulfilment of existing contracts meant that they retained a small presence in the Randgnid system, including a brief period as station managers there, until June 3306. This policy has generally allowed them to invest more in their own local operations.</p>
